    "In comparison to the MOSS 002 sft data, this collection aligns more closely with the distribution of real user intents.",
    "Furthermore, it features more detailed category labels, a broader range of harmless data, and longer dialogue sequences.",
    "• MOSS 003 sft plugin data (Sun et al, 2023b).",
    "The MOSS 003 sft plugin data dataset is an augmented version of MOSS 003 sft data, comprising around 300K multi-turn dialogue instances.",
    "It is generated by four plugins: search engine, diagram generator, calculator, and equation solver."
